rs]] ([[David Coleman (Australian politician)|David Coleman]])\n##[[Minister for Health and Aged Care#List of assistant ministers for health and aged care|Minister for Senior Australians and Aged Care]] and [[Minister for Indigenous Health]] ([[Ken Wyatt]])\n##[[Minister for Human Services|Minister for Human Services and Digital Transformation]] ([[Michael Keenan]])\n##Assistant Minister to the Prime Minister ([[Steve Irons]])\n##Assistant Minister for Regional Development and Territories ([[Sussan Ley]])\n##Assistant Minister to the Deputy Prime Minister ([[Andrew Broad]])\n##[[Minister for Transport (Australia)#List of assistant ministers for Transport|Assistant Minister for Roads and Transport]] ([[Scott Buchholz]])\n##Assistant Minister for Treasury and Finance ([[Zed Seselja]])\n##[[Minister for Defence (Australia)#List of junior ministers within the portfolio|Assistant Minister for Defence]] ([[David Fawcett]])\n##[[Minister for Foreign Affairs#List of assistant Foreign Affairs ministers|Assistant Minister for International Development and the Pacific]] ([[Anne Ruston]])\n##Assistant Minister for Trade, Tourism and Investment ([[Mark Coulton]])\n##Assistant Minister for Home Affairs ([[Linda Reynolds]])\n##[[Minister for Social Services (Australia)#List of assistant ministers for Social Services, Housing and Disability Services|Assistant Minister for Social Services, Housing and Disability Services]] ([[Sarah Henderson]])\n##Assistant Minister for Children and Families ([[Michelle Landry]])\n##Assistant Minister for Agriculture and Water Resources ([[Richard Colbeck]])\n#[[Administrator (Australia)|Administrators]] of Territories in order of appointment:\n##[[List of administrative heads of Norfolk Island|Administrator of Norfolk Island]] ([[Eric Hutchinson (politician)|Eric Hutchinson]]) (1 April 2017)\n## Administrator of the [[Australian Indian Ocean Territories]] ([[Natasha Griggs]]) (5 October 2017)\n## [[Administrator of the Northern Territory]] ([[Vicki