ish Masters|1R]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Ranking Event\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|NH\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2007 Irish Masters|RR]]\n| colspan=\"16\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[World Series of Snooker|World Series Grand Final]]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"29\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[World Series of Snooker 2008/2009#World Series of Snooker Grand Final|2R]]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"30\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[World Series of Snooker|World Series Killarney]]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"30\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:thistle;\"|[[World Series of Snooker 2009/2010#World Series of Snooker \u2013 Killarney|F]]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"30\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[World Series of Snooker|World Series Prague]]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"30\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#00ff00;\"|[[World Series of Snooker 2009/2010#World Series of Snooker \u2013 Prague|'''W''']]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"30\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[Power Snooker]]\n| colspan=\"31\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2010 Power Snooker Masters Trophy|QF]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n| colspan=\"31\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[Premier League Snooker|Premier League]]<ref group=\"nb\">The event was also called the Professional Snooker League (1983/1984), Matchroom League (1986/1987 to 1991/1992) 